lookup.description: United Pursuit - Garden LiveUnited PursuitLabel: KingswayDescription: PRODUKTBESCHREIBUNGEN Recorded between 2013 - 2015 'Garden (Live)' is a 12-track double album featuring original early recordings of the songs from their studio album 'Garden'. As they gathered weekly to worship as a community these were the spontaneous songs and refrains that carried the flame of their passion for God. These early not-quite-complete versions are exactly what people love about United Pursuit and this release has been prompted by requests from their followers to hear how the fully grown 'Garden' studio versions began. The songs are real raw and vulnerable. They are prayers and reminders intercession and intimacy.

lookup.description: The Message Trust is a Christian charity working to improve the lives of young people in Greater Manchester UK and beyond With a history of great musical initiatives such as The World Wide Message Tribe and LZ7 it is no surprise that new songs and sounds are flourishing Worship leaders and musicians gathered in Manchester in September 2015 together with a packed crowd for a meaningful and Inspiring worship event The CD is split into 3 movements - A Call To Worship A Call To Live Deep A Call To Go and each movement features 4 songs preceded by a spoken word One of the spoken contributors is Andy Hawthorne founder of The Message Trust and awarded an OBE for services to young people.

lookup.title: How to Be a Great Sound Engineer in Your Church DVD
lookup.description: How To Be a Great Sound Engineer In Your Church features over two hours of superb teaching from one of the UK's most enduring PA specialists Brian Hillson brings over 40 years of experience as a live sound engineer to help you train your Church Worship team Discover with practical demonstrations how different microphones work how to get the best out of the mixer and choose the correct loudspeakers Resolve the issues of intelligibility in difficult acoustics mic selection feedback EQ and learn new techniques to run effective sound checks Discover that you are as much of an instrument of worship in your role in PA as is a musician is on the stage one integrated team working together to bring excellence to the worship experience This practical step by step guide will benefit everyone who serves the church in the worship team and will be an excellent resource to use as part of your training.

lookup.title: Intersect
lookup.description: Intersect Where your story and God's story converge is a five week short-film resource to help you engage others in spiritual conversations Intersect is a series of videos that uses the creative medium of video-storytelling to discuss where your story and God's story converge We all have stories Some of them are joyous and easy to share with the world Others are difficult and remind us of times that we sometimes wish we could simply forget But nonetheless we have unique and beautiful lives that are marked by events situations and circumstances that make us who we are today Each session in this series takes a look at a specific issue that we all experience at some point in our lives Whether it be expectations rest disappointment trust or control human beings have the propensity to find themselves in the middle of situations that are trying It is our response to these times that help define our lives Track list Control Disappointment Expectations Rest Winds A resource from T.

lookup.title: Kim Walker-Smith on My Side (CD)
lookup.description: On My SideKim Walker-SmithLabel: Jesus CultureDescription: Kim Walker-Smith is one of the most influential female voices in worship music. Fans around the world have come to love her passionate and uninhibited sound captured on live recordings from Jesus Culture. Kim's latest full-length album ON MY SIDE is her first solo studio project exploring themes of heartbreak and triumph and giving the listener a glimpse into the past few years in her journey with God. Although a departure from her live recordings Kim's unforgettable soulful voice continues to capture exhilarating moments of worship through both nuance and strength as she weaves together this beautiful collection of songs.

With 11 original tracks Bryan and Katie bring their songwriting strengths yet again as they did in their debut album Here on Earth. lookup.title: NewWine Worship 20 Year Collection CD
lookup.description: Live Worship From NewWine - 20 Year Collection - Featuring: Sam Bailey Eoghan Heaslip Tim Hughnes Matt Redman David Ruis Martin Smith & Susie Woodbridge / Integrity Music Audio CD 2016 / 67812 UPC 0000768678121 CD Description: Live Worship From NewWine - 20 Year Collection is a profound and spirited audio CD released by Integrity Music in 2016 bearing the UPC 0000768678121. This compilation is a celebratory anthology of live worship recordings marking two decades of NewWine s influential presence in Christian worship music. The album features a stellar lineup of worship leaders and artists like Sam Bailey Eoghan Heaslip Tim Hughes Matt Redman David Ruis Martin Smith and Susie Woodbridge each bringing their unique voice and style to this collection. Album Highlights: Great Is Your Faithfulness (Unchanging) - A classic hymn reimagined with contemporary fervor. Light Of The World (Feat. Tim Hughes) - A deeply moving track that highlights Jesus as the light in darkness. The Heart Of Worship (Feat. Matt Redman) - An iconic song that returns to the heart of worship being all about Jesus. God s Great Dance Floor (Feat. Martin Smith) - An exuberant celebration of God s joy and freedom. Oceans (Feat. Susie Woodbridge) - A powerful rendition invoking trust and faith in God s guidance. Special Features: Diverse Worship Styles: The album showcases a variety of worship music styles from introspective ballads to uplifting anthems. Celebration of Legacy: It marks 20 years of NewWine s impact in the Christian worship scene. Collaborative Spirit: Features collaborative performances by some of the most renowned artists in contemporary Christian music. Live Recording Authenticity: Captures the raw unfiltered energy and spirit of live worship. Purpose and Audience: Live Worship From NewWine - 20 Year Collection is ideal for those who appreciate live worship music and enjoy a variety of worship leaders and styles. It s perfect for personal times of worship church gatherings or anyone looking to experience a sense of communal worship through music. The album serves as a great introduction to NewWine s impact over the years and is a fitting collection for long-time fans as well as newcomers to contemporary Christian music.

lookup.title: Lion of Judah DVD
lookup.description: The Lion of Judah a laugh-filled heart warming story seen through the eyes of a zany cast of stable animals Take an eye-opening adventure with a lovable pig Horace a faint-hearted horse Monty a finicky rat Slink a rambling rooster Drake a motherly cow Esmay a downtrodden donkey Jack and a heroic lamb Judah and you have got a classic in the making Upon learning that Judah has been trapped in the clutches of the townspeople and faces the possibility of being the sacrifice at the annual Festival the stablemates leave their cosy barn and embark on a hilariously funny series of adventures to find and free their friend During their numerous attempts to find Judah a wonderful story emerges as they intercept interact and entwine with history finally seeking out the King who was born in their stable more than 30 years earlier The antics of our unique cast crates a uniquely funny and entertaining epic as it winds its way through numerous side-splitting encounters.

lookup.title: Taming the Tiger DVD Tony Anthony Author
lookup.description: This fast-paced, compelling and chilling account is the deeply moving story of a three-time Kung Fu World Champion. With fascinating insight into the traditions of China's martial arts, it documents the abusive upbringing that turned a four-year-old child into a hardened, professional killer. From China to Europe and across the Mediterranean, we follow Tony as he becomes an elite bodyguard, protecting some of the world's most powerful people. Following personal tragedy, Tony's extreme discipline and the philosophy of his art is quickly turned. He begins to use his skills for illegal means and highly destructive, bloodthirsty pleasure. Eventually incarcerated in jail in Cyprus, Tony hits rock bottom. Through the visits of a stranger, he is introduced to the reality and life-changing power of Jesus Christ. Though the prison walls hold him, he finds himself a free man. This is just the beginning of a complex and fascinating testimony. This DVD features live footage of Tony Anthony sharing his amazing story interspersed with 'docudrama' footage. This unique presentation (about an hour long) brings to life the story of 'Taming the Tiger' (and the children's edition 'Cry of the Tiger') and is a must for all fans of the book as well as being an excellent outreach tool.The book 'Taming the Tiger' has now sold almost 100,000 copies and has been translated into 17 languages. It won the 'CBC Book of the Year' award and the 2006 'CBA Biography of the Year'.

lookup.title: Made For You
lookup.description: If you’ve spent any time listening to Christian music, the chances are you’ve already heard Lou Fellingham sing. Not only as a songwriter and worship leader but as a woman who has been an ever-present in the music industry for the last 20 years. An internationally known worship leader, six albums in to a firmly-established ministry, she is known for her prophetic edge, distinctive voice, unwavering energy to see lives changed through the power of music and word. With a heart that longs for people to know God and his outrageous love, Lou is tireless in her pursuit to write and record powerful songs and to lead people in singing truth that lifts their heads and stirs their hearts. Her critically acclaimed albums are packed with inspiring melodies wrapped around God exalting lyrics to remind us of who He is and who He has made us to be. ‘Ultimately we want the music we write to draw people to God. That by the power and presence of His Spirit people would have revelation of all that Jesus has done for us. That we can be restored to the Father. Worship is His gift to us. We’re made to worship our creator and He is worthy no matter what, but we find that as we give, we also receive.” Embodying authenticity, spiritual integrity and communicating the power of the gospel has always been the anchor of her music, underpinning and emphasizing her musical gifting.
